"That... must be a pretty bad symptom," Ishii said. [l][r]
"Hmm, I guess so," I replied vaguely. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r] “But even if I went to the hospital, there was no way to explain the cause.” [r]
"Well, that's true..." [l][r]
I was lying on the bed in my room, enjoying the phone call with Ishii that had become a habit. [l][r]
"Are you okay? Are you sleeping properly? Yes, the test results are..." [r]
"It's okay." [l][r]
I reply looking like I'm having trouble, but I can't help but smile a little. It's good because they won't find out if it's over the phone. [l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
I feel bad for Ishii, but Ishii is just a little funny when he's worried about me. [l][r]
It wasn't for that reason, but I made it a point to talk to Ishi about all the things that I would normally find difficult to talk about with other people, such as my loneliness, my guilt, and the physical and mental health problems that were probably caused by such things. [l][r]
[r]Kanazawa also said, ``It's easier to have people listen to you than to have them speak to you.'' [r]
...These are words filled with real feeling. [l][r]
In fact, I feel like it made me feel a lot better. Before I met Ishii, I would have trouble standing up or sleeping without any warning signs. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
"That's right, the other day we talked about going to Nagano." [l][r]
“Oh, what do your parents say?” [r]
“I wish I could get into university” [l][r]
"Well, I guess so. We'll need about two nights..." [r]
“I wanted to go.” [l][r]
"You can go. Taking the entrance exam will be easy for you, right?" [r]
“No, I wanted to go right away [r]
Yo” [l][r]
"I'm so happy that you're looking forward to it." [l][r]
Ishii says in a truly happy voice. She's a cute person. [l][r]
It was the same when I was making airplanes.
It seems like when Ishii is obsessed with something, he gets so absorbed in it that he can't see anything else, and he can't hide his emotions. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]

In other words, Ishii cares about me that much. Also, about you. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

