[r]I'm happy. [l][r]
I don't know how far apart Yu and I are right now, but if Ishii thinks about us together, that means we can be in the same place at that time. [l][r]
Who said this, "Thought is faster than light"? [l][r]
Honestly, I think that's just idealism. Still, it's true that I feel happy. [l][r]
I'm sure he will take good care of those feelings. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

